  "title": "Junior event crew",
  "description": "<p>🌟Junior Event Crew!!!!🌟<br /></p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for hardworking and enthusiastic individuals to join our team as Junior Event Crew. In this role, you will assist with setting up, running, and packing down events while supporting the event team with general tasks. This position is great for beginners who want to gain experience in events and hospitality.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Support event staff during events with tasks such as crowd assistance, registration, or guiding guests</li><li>Help maintain a clean and organized event area</li><li>Follow instructions from senior event staff and supervisors</li><li>Perform basic operational tasks as needed throughout the event</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Positive attitude and willingness to learn</li><li>Good teamwork and communication skills</li><li>Ability to follow instructions and work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Able to lift light equipment and stand for long periods</li><li>Reliable and punctual</li></ul>",
